  "Marcos Galperin is founder and CEO of e-commerce platform MercadoLibre, the eBay of Latin America.",
  "MercadoLibre, which operates in 18 Latin American countries and Portugal, went public in 2007 on the Nasdaq.",
  "Galperin majored in economics and finance at the University of Pennsylvania and got an MBA from Stanford University.",
  "He worked at Argentine oil company YPF for three years and as a summer intern at JPMorgan before starting MercadoLibre in 1999."
